BuildArch:      noarch

%description
Pure Java implementation of libzmq.

%package        javadoc
Summary:        Javadoc for %{name}
Group:          Documentation/HTML

%description javadoc
This package contains the API documentation for %{name}.

%prep
%setup -q
%pom_remove_plugin :maven-checkstyle-plugin
